e important than the other.  I put my starting points in STR (way back when...), and that was STUPID!!<br><br>Re: armor class--no--PoP HAS made AC relevant again.  Make no mistake about it.  Look it up on the Steel Warrior board.  Or, if you want to look noob like NOOB_001 above, go on the board and tell them that AC over 1250 is irrelevant.<br><br>Re: vision.  It doesnt matter if anyone that plays a vision-impaired class wants to admit it or not---NOT having at least basic infravision IS a drawback.  Furthermore, it CAN be easy to be of mid-to high level and NOT be wearing a vision-enhancing item.  Therefore, on RAIDS, you will find yourself NEEDING to scrap a good buff for a TURD vision buff.  Ive SEEN it happen--dont tell me it doesnt (nowadays, however, grp acumen is commonly cast...).<br><br>Gnomes as SHD--love em or hate em--they make TERRIFIC SHD..   =)<br><br>Luna<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Jul 16 13:56:48 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
